1
00:00:00,087 --> 00:00:06,225
JavaScript classes include methods that define actions the objects created from the class can perform

2
00:00:06,625 --> 00:00:12,037
The use of static methods and getters/setters further enhances class functionality

3
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:15,387
Static methods are called on the class itself

4
00:00:15,787 --> 00:00:20,562
whereas getters and setters offer a way to intercept property access and assignments

5
00:00:20,950 --> 00:00:26,137
making class usage more intuitive and safer by providing controlled access to properties

